aredi-draft-law/0000018f-01dc-d64a-a9af-85ffa1aa0000</guid></item><item><title>从以色列到伊朗：全球武器贸易报告中缺失的数据</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-world-doesnt-knows-the-full-scope-of-the-global-arms-trade/0000018f-0023-db32-a58f-fca7bccd0000</link><description>世界各地的决策者和媒体将瑞典智库 SIPRI 的年度报告视为全球武器贸易全面、可靠的信息来源。然而，它提供的数据有太多漏洞</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 18:49:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-world-doesnt-knows-the-full-scope-of-the-global-arms-trade/0000018f-0023-db32-a58f-fca7bccd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和美国官员表示，由于本-格维尔和斯莫特里奇的行为而实施新制裁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-u-s-officials-say-new-sanctions-due-to-conduct-of-ben-gvir-smotrich/0000018f-018b-d6a0-a9ef-c19f11020000</link><description>一位美国消息人士称，极右翼部长本身也被考虑实施制裁，但白宫担心双边关系受到影响。一些美国人士反对使用“制裁”一词，并表示美国只是让以色列遵守其对所有受援国的标准</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 18:13:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-u-s-officials-say-new-sanctions-due-to-conduct-of-ben-gvir-smotrich/0000018f-018b-d6a0-a9ef-c19f11020000</guid></item><item><title>以色列将得到援助，但其在华盛顿的地位从未如此动摇</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-21/ty-article/.highlight/israel-will-get-its-aid-but-its-standing-in-washington-has-never-been-shakier/0000018f-01ac-db32-a58f-fdaf995f0000</link><description>在以色列历史上最严重的生存危机中，投票反对向以色列提供紧急军事援助，这发出了一个不可否认的信息，表明以色列在民主党中的地位。共和党人不应该声称这次投票证明他们是无可争议的“亲以色列”政党</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 17:46:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-21/ty-article/.highlight/israel-will-get-its-aid-but-its-standing-in-washington-has-never-been-shakier/0000018f-01ac-db32-a58f-fdaf995f0000</guid></item><item><title>谁写了逾越节哈加达？</title><link>ht